    "summary": "helpscout.net exposes two authenticated REST APIs on subdomains (`api.helpscout.net` Inbox API via OAuth 2 and `docsapi.helpscout.net` Docs API via Basic-auth API key), plus public npm developer packages for building Help Scout Apps.",
