        "generateUrl": "https://secure.helpscout.net",
        "setup": "To create a sidebar App secret, sign in to Help Scout as an administrator or account owner, go to **Manage > Apps**, click **Create**, then **Create App**. In the app form, enter a **Secret Key** value; Help Scout uses this shared secret to sign requests sent to your app callback URL. See [Apps getting started](https://developer.helpscout.com/apps/getting-started/) and [Signature validation](https://developer.helpscout.com/apps/guides/signature-validation/)."
      }
